e-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;joint&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;）由一对法兰、一个垫片及若干个螺栓螺母组成。垫片放在两法兰密封面之间，拧紧螺母后，垫片表面上的比压达到一定数值后产生变形，并填满密封面上凹凸不平处，使联接严密不漏。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, SimSun; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p0&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, SimSun; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft yahei&amp;quot;; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploads/ueditor/20200402/5e858dd97b432.png&quot; title=&quot;ds.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;ds.jpg&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; mar